description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 250, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Leverage for East, Leverage for South, and 8 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40505-46682-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [250 Votes, Top 5% Score]
